title: Enjoi 8-Bit Series featuring Caswell Berry
description:
In a world of 8-bit pixels, Caswell Berry stars as "8-Bit Larry" in this thumb blister quest to be number one in the podium of life.
Co-Starring Louie Barletta and Cairo Foster with special appearances by Jose Rojo and Zack Wallin as THE MEAT!
